videos.headline: Wimbush, Davis connect again for 2nd TD
videos.description: UCF extends its lead to 27-0 on Brandon Wimbush's 12-yard touchdown strike to Gabriel Davis for their second scoring connection of the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wimbush, Davis connect again for 2nd TD) 2019/8/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCF's Harris hauls in Gabriel's 3rd TD pass
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel stays composed on a botched snap and finds Alex Harris wide open for a 26-yard score, his third touchdown toss of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCF’s Harris hauls in Gabriel's 3rd TD pass) 2019/8/29 ESHEET
